title: 'Numerous' fatalities after shooting at Florida high school
text:
'Numerous' fatalities after shooting at Florida high school 6:27am IST - 02:36 
A shooter opened fire in a Florida high school on Wednesday morning, killing multiple people and sending hundreds of panicked students fleeing into the streets while others huddled in classrooms as police hunted for the gunman. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
